pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: left-accent
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [0, 0, 8, 720]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$secondary"
  - elementId: product-badge
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [60, 35, 145, 28]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: badge-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 35, 145, 28]
    content:
      text: "REGENERATIVE"
      fontSize: 11
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$light"
      letterSpacing: 1
      align: [center, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 75, 600, 40]
    content:
      style: "$pageTitle"
      text: "TB-500  —  Overview"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: divider
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    bounds: [60, 120, 1160, 0]
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E6F1FB"
  - elementId: col1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 140, 300, 25]
    content:
      text: "DESCRIPTION"
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$secondary"
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: col1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 175, 550, 195]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>TB-500 is the synthetic version of Thymosin Beta-4 (TB4), a 43-amino acid peptide found in virtually all human and animal cells. The predominant thymosin in the body.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:10px">Plays a fundamental role in wound healing, angiogenesis, and cell migration. Often stacked with BPC-157 for comprehensive tissue repair protocols.</p>
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: col2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 140, 300, 25]
    content:
      text: "MECHANISM OF ACTION"
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$secondary"
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: mech-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [660, 175, 560, 195]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.6
      text: |
        <p>Core regenerative mechanisms:</p>
        <ul>
        <li>Upregulates actin polymerization</li>
        <li>Promotes endothelial cell migration</li>
        <li>Reduces inflammatory cytokines</li>
        <li>Stimulates stem cell differentiation</li>
        <li>Enhances cell-to-cell communication</li>
        </ul>
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: clinical-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 395, 300, 25]
    content:
      text: "RESEARCH HIGHLIGHTS"
      fontSize: 14
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      color: "$secondary"
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: data-card-1-bg
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [60, 430, 250, 100]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E6F1FB"
  - elementId: data-1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [75, 440, 220, 45]
    content:
      style: "$dataHighlight"
      text: "43-aa"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: data-1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [75, 490, 220, 30]
    content:
      style: "$label"
      text: "Amino acid chain"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: data-card-2-bg
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [330, 430, 250, 100]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E6F1FB"
  - elementId: data-2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [345, 440, 220, 45]
    content:
      style: "$dataHighlight"
      text: "Actin"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: data-2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [345, 490, 220, 30]
    content:
      style: "$label"
      text: "Key structural protein regulated"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: data-card-3-bg
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [600, 430, 250, 100]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E6F1FB"
  - elementId: data-3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [615, 440, 220, 45]
    content:
      style: "$dataHighlight"
      text: "Systemic"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
  - elementId: data-3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [615, 490, 220, 30]
    content:
      style: "$label"
      text: "Works throughout the body"
      lineHeight: 1.3
      align: [left, top]
  - elementId: data-card-4-bg
    elementType: shape
    shapeName: rect
    bounds: [870, 430, 350, 100]
